{"type":"message-part","messageId":"31c3d2b5-b83f-4525-9710-f2b5d69954d6","role":"user","index":0,"part":{"type":"text","text":"# Preserving your work\n\nSave a copy of files you create during this task to `/logs/artifacts/`. This directory is preserved after the run so outputs can be inspected. Organize with subdirectories if helpful (e.g., `/logs/artifacts/code/`, `/logs/artifacts/reports/`). The directory already exists and is writable.\n\n---\n\n# Windmill Script Metadata YAML\n\n## Background\nWindmill uses companion `.script.yaml` files to describe a script's schema, summary, description, language, and template status. These metadata files allow Windmill to validate inputs, render a UI form, and document the script without running it.\n\nYou have a pre-existing TypeScript script at `/home/user/windmill-project/f/analytics/report.ts`:\n\n```typescript\nexport async function main(start_date: string, end_date: string, limit: number = 100) {\n  return { start_date, end_date, limit, report: \"placeholder\" };\n}\n```\n\n## Requirements\nCreate a companion metadata file `f/analytics/report.script.yaml` inside the project directory `/home/user/windmill-project` with the following content:\n\n1. `summary`: `\"Generate analytics report\"`\n2. `description`: `\"Generates a date-range analytics report with configurable row limit\"`\n3. `schema` with three properties:\n   - `start_date`: type `string`, required\n   - `end_date`: type `string`, required\n   - `limit`: type `integer`, default `100`, **not** required\n4. `language`: `bun`\n5. `is_template`: `false`\n\n## Implementation Guide\n\n1. Navigate to the project directory:\n   ```bash\n   cd /home/user/windmill-project\n   ```\n2. Create the metadata file `f/analytics/report.script.yaml` with the correct YAML content. You may write the file directly — no `wmill` CLI command is needed to produce a metadata file. Example structure:\n   ```yaml\n   summary: \"Generate analytics report\"\n   description: \"Generates a date-range analytics report with configurable row limit\"\n   schema:\n     $schema: \"https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema\"\n     type: object\n     properties:\n       start_date:\n         type: string\n         description: \"Start date for the report range\"\n       end_date:\n         type: string\n         description: \"End date for the report range\"\n       limit:\n         type: integer\n         description: \"Maximum number of rows to return\"\n         default: 100\n     required:\n       - start_date\n       - end_date\n   is_template: false\n   language: bun\n   ```\n\n## Constraints\n- Project path: `/home/user/windmill-project`\n- The metadata file must be located at `f/analytics/report.script.yaml` relative to the project root.\n- Do NOT modify `report.ts`.\n- No live Windmill server is required — only the local file needs to be created."}}
